graph TD
    classDef client fill:#3b82f6,stroke:#1d4ed8,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff;
    classDef api fill:#10b981,stroke:#047857,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff;
    classDef external fill:#f59e0b,stroke:#b45309,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff;
    classDef database fill:#8b5cf6,stroke:#6d28d9,stroke-width:2px,color:#fff;

    %% Client Layer
    User([User]) -->|1. Uploads Product Image & Market Config| UI[Next.js Frontend]:::client
    UI -->|2. Dispatch Action| Pipeline[useGeneration Pipeline]:::client

    %% Phase 1: Analyze & Extract
    subgraph "Phase 1: Profile Extraction (/api/analyze-extract)"
        Pipeline -->|3. POST Image & Hint| API_Analyze[Analyze API Route]:::api
        
        %% Parallel Tasks
        API_Analyze -->|4a. Remove Background| Photoroom[Photoroom API]:::external
        Photoroom -->|Transparent PNG| Supabase[(Supabase Storage)]:::database
        Supabase -->|Public URL| API_Analyze
        
        API_Analyze -->|4b. Analyze Visuals| GeminiVision[Vertex AI: Gemini 2.5 Flash]:::external
        GeminiVision -->|JSON: Materials, Features, Style| API_Analyze
    end

    %% Phase 2: Generation
    subgraph "Phase 2: Content Generation (/api/generate-pack)"
        API_Analyze -->|5. Pass Product Profile + Image URL| API_Generate[Generate API Route]:::api
        
        %% Creative Director
        API_Generate -->|6. Act as Creative Director| GeminiCreative[Vertex AI: Gemini 2.5 Flash]:::external
        GeminiCreative -->|7. JSON: 6 Scenes, SEO, Ad Copy| API_Generate
        
        %% Batched Rendering
        API_Generate -->|8. Fetch Product Base64| API_Generate
        API_Generate -->|9. Batched Requests (2 at a time)| GeminiImage[Vertex AI: Gemini 2.5 Flash-Image]:::external
        
        GeminiImage -.->|10. Quota Reached| Retry{Auto Retry}
        Retry -.->|6s Backoff| GeminiImage
        GeminiImage -->|11. Final Product-in-Scene Images| API_Generate
    end

    %% Return Results
    API_Generate -->|12. Return Final Pack Payload| Pipeline
    Pipeline -->|13. Update State| UI
    UI -->|14. Display Dashboard/Pack| User
